{"tid":2208762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"去留立會激辯 楊岳橋：擋清算 梁晃維：太樂觀","createTime":"2020-09-19T07:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T09:48:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"337d1a4932a5fa938186cf9f9c7207798b7b773d","tid":2208762,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:13:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200919/K2XYM2O7FRHVZIICF335WHDWAQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200919%2FK2XYM2O7FRHVZIICF335WHDWAQ%2F&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdChYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=9d0ef8e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200919%2FK2XYM2O7FRHVZIICF335WHDWAQ%2F&h=de4fea44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200919/K2XYM2O7FRHVZIICF335WHDWAQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n去留立會激辯 楊岳橋：擋清算 梁晃維：太樂觀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JlThk4TeE3hHKZQCXDfOm1ZyvEo=/578x327/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YYI4I55PFNE2LLHBG2VTEMBOSU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJlThk4TeE3hHKZQCXDfOm1ZyvEo%3D%2F578x327%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYYI4I55PFNE2LLHBG2VTEMBOSU.gif&h=fb99a6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■楊岳橋認為民主派留任議會，可拉布阻擋梁美芬利用權力及特權法清算抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】主留派與杯葛派昨晚就民主派立法會去留問題展開激辯，傾向延任一年的公民黨楊岳橋、民主黨林卓廷、社民連岑子杰質疑杯葛派只着眼於委任性的原則問題，惟無法解釋民主派議員離任議會後可以如何阻擋經民聯梁美芬利用《立法會（權力及特權）條例》全面清算抗爭者，亦無法提供議會外為港人爭取訴求的清晰路線圖。傾向杯葛的泛民初選勝出者梁晃維、岑敖暉與劉頴匡反駁指，接受中共委任等同合理化中共行為、令港府恢復選舉的張力減低，惟岑敖暉承認，目前確實未能提供撤出議會後的路線圖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n查抗爭資金來源議案料續審<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬去年以《立法會（權力及特權）條例》要求立法會成立專責委員會，調查抗爭者的資金及物資來源，議案料在「臨立會」繼續審議。楊岳橋認為，民主派留在議會可繼續利用議事規則就議案提出質詢，與建制派拉布，阻擋梁美芬以特權法全面清算、凌辱抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋指一旦民主派撤出議會，專責委員會成員便會全數由建制派擔任，「過去一年民主運動係光明正大，但唔代表每一個捐錢嘅人都希望將賬目公開畀保皇黨睇」，擔心在建制派。。。。。。。。。。。線。<br />\n<br />\n梁晃維反駁指，港府聯同警方可隨時清算港人，形容主留派的想法「太樂觀」，並指港人不應局限自身想像，以為只能運用議員一職才能繼續推動民主運動。岑敖暉補充指，若民。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Mkun_HGc8LXuC4oH3c4H2X1DR-U=/578x327/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OORODEPPYZD2HNTCXERJQ4RUNI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMkun_HGc8LXuC4oH3c4H2X1DR-U%3D%2F578x327%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOORODEPPYZD2HNTCXERJQ4RUNI.gif&h=9bac24d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■岑敖暉憂慮若議員延任將減低國際關注，難迫令政府盡快恢復選舉。"},{"pid":"a3c5e587bcfdf87738d415852a2193b805d08dcf","tid":2208762,"uid":3976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:22:09.000Z","msg":"拉布咁有效就唔會過去一直比d惡法過到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7da8d07e6ffb7221652959d226d02eb4609f36","tid":2208762,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:26:39.000Z","msg":"呢度有得睇番<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nD100 link<br />\n【延任議會．去留之辯】<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VAv3kLUSwn0SAVE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVAv3kLUSwn0SAVE&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdChYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=f01c59b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VAv3kLUSwn0SAVE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#Appledaily #StayHome #WithMe<br />\n延任議會●去留之辯論壇︱主留VS杯葛 3對3激辯！ (蘋果日報 Apple Daily)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SSymfqTD-ww\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSSymfqTD-ww&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdChYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=c6ff7bb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SSymfqTD-ww</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立場 link<br />\n【延任議會 去留之辯】<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3nvyd0A0t1Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3nvyd0A0t1Q&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdChYTjY4AGk5vq